You have to do a lot of things and repeat them weekly.
I'm facing similar situations as a manager, in terms of stress and pressure, but I feel like it's the right role for me.
I always wanted to be a manager, and now that I can do that, I feel like it's the best thing that's going to happen to me in my entire adult life.
